    {
      "sender_name": "Avour \u00f0\u009f\u0099\u0088\u00f0\u009f\u00a4\u008d",
      "timestamp_ms": 1769422842683,
      "content": "Avour sent an attachment.",
      "share": {
        "link": "https://www.instagram.com/reel/DN9_btPiLAq/?id=3710400648958226474_66343168926",
        "share_text": "If you\u00e2\u0080\u0099ve ever waited all day just for them to say \u00e2\u0080\u009cI\u00e2\u0080\u0099m too tired to talk,\u00e2\u0080\u009d read this \u00e2\u00ac\u0087\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\nI\u00e2\u0080\u0099ve felt this too, and it can sting \u00e2\u0080\u0094 but here\u00e2\u0080\u0099s how I learned to handle it better:\n\n1\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00e2\u0083\u00a3 Talk about expectations. I told my partner that even a 5\u00e2\u0080\u009310 min call means a lot after a long day. That way, I\u00e2\u0080\u0099m not left disappointed.\u00e2\u0080\u00a82\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00e2\u0083\u00a3 Find small \u00e2\u0080\u009cconnection hacks.\u00e2\u0080\u009d If he\u00e2\u0080\u0099s too tired to talk, I\u00e2\u0080\u0099ll ask him to send me a quick voice note or \u00e2\u0080\u009cgoodnight selfie\u00e2\u0080\u009d so I still feel close.\u00e2\u0080\u00a83\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00e2\u0083\u00a3 Use the time for yourself. Instead of spiraling, I started journaling little things I wanted to tell him tomorrow. It helps me channel the missing energy.\u00e2\u0080\u00a84\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00e2\u0083\u00a3 Remember it\u00e2\u0080\u0099s not rejection. Most of the time, they\u00e2\u0080\u0099re really just tired \u00e2\u0080\u0094 not tired of you. Framing it that way saved me a lot of hurt feelings.\u00e2\u0080\u00a85\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00e2\u0083\u00a3 Final tip (important): Long-distance couples often struggle because of unmet expectations \u00e2\u0080\u0094 and that\u00e2\u0080\u0099s why 70% don\u00e2\u0080\u0099t last. If you want to be in the 30% that do, check the link in my bio for the full guide \u00e2\u009d\u00a4\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\n\n\u00f0\u009f\u008e\u00a5: love4infinity on TikTok \u00e2\u0080\u00a8\n\n#ldr #longdistancerelationship #ldrquotes #ldrproblems #relationshiptips #longdistancecouple #couplegoals",
